---
// Hero.astro - Landing VE
---
<main class="relative pt-32 pb-20 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[700px] h-[700px] blur-[120px] opacity-30 animate-pulse-slow pointer-events-none"
       style="background: conic-gradient(from 180deg at 50% 50%, #7c3aed66 0deg, #00ffcc33 120deg, #b026ff66 240deg, #7c3aed66 360deg);">
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04]" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-0 w-full h-px bg-ve-purple"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-2/4 left-0 w-full h-px bg-ve-purple"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-3/4 left-0 w-full h-px bg-ve-purple"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-px h-full bg-ve-purple"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-2/4 w-px h-full bg-ve-purple"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-3/4 w-px h-full bg-ve-purple"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
      <span class="ve-eyebrow" data-c="t1">
        <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-ve-text align-middle mr-2 animate-pulse"></span>
        // 01 // martes - Hecho en Venezuela
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-[7.5rem] font-sans leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter mb-10">
      <span class="font-extralight text-ve-text block">Tu negocio,</span>
      <span class="font-black italic text-ve-text block mt-2" style="background: linear-gradient(120deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 35%, #ec4899 70%, #f97316 100%); background-size: 200% 200%; -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent; animation: hero-shimmer 5s ease-in-out infinite; padding-right: 0.15em;">sin el caos.</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-ve-muted leading-[1.7] font-light ve-justified">
        <span class="font-medium text-ve-text">martes</span> se conecta a tu negocio tal como esta hoy &mdash; tu facturacion, tu WhatsApp, tu libreta, tu Excel. No tienes que cambiar nada. Te damos <span class="font-semibold text-ve-text">agentes AI que trabajan 24/7</span>: organizan cobros, generan reportes, atienden clientes, ejecutan marketing. Llevamos tu operacion a otro nivel.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-12">
      <a href="https://wa.me/584120000000?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20empezar%20con%20martes" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-ve-purple text-white hover:bg-ve-purple-deep font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] transition-all text-sm shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5"
         style="box-shadow: 0 8px 30px -8px rgba(124,58,237,0.5);">
        Empezar por WhatsApp
        <svg class="ml-3 w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-ve-muted font-medium tracking-wide">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cat-t1 animate-pulse"></span>
      INTEGRADO PARA VENEZUELA
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
